+3. **Symptom amnesia.** Symptoms selectively forgotten mid-hunt. → the **frozen symptom ledger**
+   (stages 0a/0b).
+4. **Confabulation.** Diagnostic code referencing variables that didn't exist. → the **cold red-team of
